    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 12. Grandaustralis boomerang. 9 — collection localities (red dots); 10 — habitat of type locality, south of Ravensthorpe, W. A.; 11 — male flight pattern; 12 — male after landing at Ravensthorpe, W. A." ;
